```

The `- 1` in the loop condition means the loop stops one index short, so the last element is always skipped. This causes 3 of the 4 Vitest tests to fail.

**Change required:** Remove `- 1` from the loop condition in `src/utils.ts`. That's the only edit needed — all 4 tests will then pass.

